data.description: Prepare to fall in love with this charming single-family home, offering the convenience of a single level living with no stairs, nestled in a tranquil and private neighborhood. As you step inside, you'll be enveloped by the warm and inviting ambiance, making it a perfect space for entertaining. This well-designed home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with the added flexibility of a converted garage space currently used as a hobby room but easily transformed into a 4th bedroom or restored to a full-sized 2-car garage. The spacious lot provides ample room for a workshop or an additional garage. The expansive backyard features a fire pit, making it an ideal spot for gatherings on crisp fall evenings. The location is unbeatable, just a short distance from Branson Landing, fishing spots, lakes, restaurants, and the entertainment scene in Branson. Moreover, you'll appreciate the charm of the tree-lined street, with new homes under construction next door, adding to the neighborhood's appeal. Don't miss the chance to make this inviting home your own!
